description:
As always, Jahy-sama can only paint herself in a positive light to Druj,
so she ends up telling her that she`s found and defeated the Magical Girl.
On top of that, the landlord has gotten into a fight with her sister and moves into Jahy-sama`s room.
Having her around is a major pain, but Jahy-sama can`t seem to get her to leave.
The landlord does offer to do some chores, but she`s even more useless than Jahy imagined!
Source: crunchyroll
